OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain or
OL,6,Fshowers, locally heavy, gradually
OL,7,Fclearing eastward this evening.
OL,8,FBecoming largely dry with clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping during the second half of
OL,10,Fthe night. Winds strengthening
OL,11,Fovernight, particularly towards the
OL,12,Fcoast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FVariable amounts of cloud but
OL,15,Fa dry, bright day for many. Gentle or
OL,16,Fmoderate breezes continue through the
OL,17,Fday, but still feeling pleasantly
OL,18,Fwarm, particularly in any sheltered
OL,19,Fspots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
